Pleb.ca Shared Cooperation Via Secure Communication.
Initiative from tactiq.net of releasing this projest as opensource for it to suck as less as possible.

Message Requirements  
	1.Communication Content 
		Array(0="string",1="string",2="string",4="string")

Encryption Requirements  
	1.Communication Content 
 	2.Shared Secret Phrase 
	3.Server side Salt

Decryption Requirements  
	1.IV
 	2.Shared Secret Phrase
	3.Server side Salt	
	4.encrypted Coop 
		
POST values
v1='server salt' String
v2='Secret phrase' String
v3='base64_encoded(json(Array))' String


In -> v1=Salt v2=Secret v3=base64_encoded (json(Array));


Out -> base64_encoded( json array('iv' => 'IV key', 'Enc' => 'Communication Content'))